<br />

<br />
We don't have "zerg" army of CLR (normally about 9, and 4-5 druids). However most individuals are skilled and never AFK, hehe.. (Just to help estimating on what awaits us -- most in the guild are time/elem geared and we have do have 48 people with Ikky4 piece, however Ikkinz was won with 31 (#1) - 41 (#4) people).
<br />

<br />
Any advice and links appreciated.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
