<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">We assigned each tank a chanter and on incoming...once the tank show up on hot we dispell,tash,slow, cripplied.  Dont tash until the tank has aggro your better off doing nothing vs dying.  We let the shammy come around later and re slow if they want to, but a lot of time mobs were dead with just our slow.  Once we were doing with the debuff trash we just nuked.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
