<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">Spectral Trushar Worshiper
<br />

<br />
hits like a truck, really mows mobs down.
<br />
With mage-summoned haste mask, a pair of weapons, and a good haste, this mob can make quick work of just about anything, enchanters included.  Its a good test of reaction time.
<br />

<br />
This mob is immune to mez, and I found AE stun to be ineffective against him.  Best to have someone else with a stun on hand to help ya.  Zerker Stun is very nice, as its insta-cast.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
